<body>
  <h1>Welcome to Book App :)</h1>
  <p>Read this to understand the usage of this application. Navigate to Add
    Author page using the above link. Create an Author of your choice just by
    entering the name of the author. Navigate to the Add book page to add any
    book you like. Dont forget to select author from the list of authors that
    you created earlier. Note that Books and Authors that you create can be
    Modified/deleted by anyone.
  </p><br />
  <h2 class="page-header">Recently added books</h2>

  {{#each books as |value key|}}
    <span>
      <a href="/books/show/{{value._id}}">
        <img
          src="/books/images/{{value._id}}"
          height="150"
          width="150"
          alt="book cover"
        />
      </a>
      <h3>{{value.title}}</h3>
    </span>
  {{/each}}
</body>